हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: When billionaire industrialist Hardeep Singh Oberoi tries to shield his daughter Mahima from heartbreak, she launches “Mission Daddy Ki Dulhan” to find him a bride. Fate brings them to the warm-hearted Srikavita Nair, whose simple values clash yet connect with Hardeep’s guarded world. But as secrets of Srikavita’s past and her abusive ex-husband Rajeev Menon surface, relationships are tested, identities are shaken, and love, trust, and family bonds must stand the ultimate test. Watch Now!
